ActEmergency Management Act
SubjectProvincial Emergency Financial Assistance Order No. 201, Saskatchewan
PrecisPROVINCIAL EMERGENCY FINANCIAL ASSISTANCE ORDER NO. 201 which makes a declaration of federal concern and authorizes the provision of financial assistance to the province of SASKATCHEWAN, with respect to the SPRING FLOOD that affected the province from March 1, 2016 to May 13, 2016.
